After using Hertz a couple times, I knew that I had to change rental car companies.  I hit the motherload.  I have heard the rumors about Enterprise...they hire a lot of college grads, they wear suits, they are friendly...yeah, yeah, yeah.  Well, the truth be told, this is the best rental car company and rental car experience I have had.  They were very quick to get through the line, upgraded me for cheap, did not try and upsell me on insurance and gas, and sent me on my way.  When I reached downstairs, a little guy in a suit grabbed me a bottle of water and took me to my car.  We did the walk around and he gave me a map and directions to the 202.  All in all, it was quick, efficient and very friendly.  I will never use Hertz again at Phoenix Sky Harbor.  Enterprise it is!

